24419: <file path="observability/metrics.md">
24420:  1: # Metrics
24421:  2: 
24422:  3: Métricas: routing accuracy, tool usage, tool misuse, tool switching, grounding quality, gaps, token efficiency, caveman effectiveness.
24423:  4: 
24424:  5: ## Optimization Metrics
24425:  6: 
24426:  7: ### Token Saver effectiveness
24427:  8: 
24428:  9: - reduced_context_used: true/false
24429: 10: - full_file_reads_avoided
24430: 11: - chunks_retrieved
24431: 12: - tool_calls_count
24432: 13: - fallback_used
24433: 14: 
24434: 15: ### Caveman effectiveness
24435: 16: 
24436: 17: - response_mode: lite/full/evidence-first/didactic-lite
24437: 18: - unnecessary_intro_removed: true/false
24438: 19: - sources_preserved: true/false
24439: 20: - user_requested_more_detail: true/false
24440: 21: 
24441: 22: ## Umbrales operativos recomendados
24442: 23: 
24443: 24: - routing_accuracy: `>= 95%`
24444: 25: - grounding_quality (casos con fuentes): `>= 90%`
24445: 26: - tool_misuse: `<= 2%`
24446: 27: - fallback_rate: `<= 10%` (si supera, revisar reglas)
24447: 28: - token_efficiency: tendencia estable o mejorando
24448: 29: - caveman_effectiveness: `>= 85%`
24449: 30: 
24450: 31: ## Semaforo
24451: 32: 
24452: 33: - `OK`: todos los umbrales en rango.
24453: 34: - `WARN`: 1-2 metricas fuera de rango.
24454: 35: - `FAIL`: 3+ metricas fuera de rango o fallo repetido de grounding/HITL.
24455: </file>
